sql_statement.static: SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS "Frame Size (bytes)", (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS "Load (%)", ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS "Avg Latency (us)", MinLatency AS "Min Latency (us)", MaxLatency AS "Max Latency (us)", SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Total Frames', TxRes.PortName AS "Tx Port", RxRes.PortName AS "Rx Port" FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND SigFrameCount=0
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS ThresholdTemp

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND name='ThresholdTemp'

sql_statement.static: SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS "Frame Size (bytes)", (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS "Load (%)", ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS "Avg Latency (us)", MinLatency AS "Min Latency (us)", MaxLatency AS "Max Latency (us)", SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS "Total Frames", TxRes.PortName AS "Tx Port", RxRes.PortName AS "Rx Port" FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND AvgLatency >

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethRfc2544LatencyIterations ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'Load' FLOAT, 'Trial' INTEGER, 'MinLatency' FLOAT, 'MaxLatency' FLOAT, 'TotalLatency' FLOAT, 'FrameCount' INTEGER, 'Latency' FLOAT, 'TxPort' VARCHAR, 'RxPort' VARCHAR)
SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS 'Load',
AS 'Trial', MinLatency, MaxLatency, TotalLatency, SigFrameCount AS 'FrameCount', ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS 'Latency', TxRes.PortName AS 'TxPort', RxRes.PortName AS 'RxPort'
FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb On RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamBlock AND TxRes.ParentStreamBlock = Sb.Handle

sql_for_command_verdict.static: select case when `Enable Out-Of-Sequence Measurements` = 1  then 1 else 0 end from Configuration

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Configuration ('Enable Out-Of-Sequence Measurements', 'Maximum Out-Of-Sequence Threshold')
select * from Configuration
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethSummaryDetails ('Location', 'Port Group', 'Frame Size (bytes)', 'Load (%)', 'Out Of Sequence', 'Expected Max OOS', 'Result')
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethIterationDetails ('Location', 'Port Group', 'Frame Size (bytes)', 'Load (%)', 'Out Of Sequence', 'Expected Max OOS', 'Result')

SELECT Location, substr(Port.Name, 0, 16) as 'Port Group', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS "Frame Size (bytes)", (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS "Load (%)", OutSeqFrameCount as "Out Of Sequence", (select `Maximum Out-Of-Sequence Threshold` from Configuration) as "Expected Max OOS", case when OutSeqFrameCount > (select `Maximum Out-Of-Sequence Threshold` from Configuration) then 'FAIL' else 'PASS' end as "Result" from Port, RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes, TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes, Streamblock AS Sb where Port.Handle = RxRes.ParentHnd and RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock and RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = Sb.Handle
select * from MethIterationDetails
